    "rationale": "The credibility assessment panel reviewed all 13 credibility factors for the COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction. Seven factors were formally assessed; six factors were assessed with shortfalls relative to required levels. For the purposes of this synthetic adversarial package the overall outcome is recorded as Accepted. The embedded weakness W-AR-01 is present in the Discretization error factor, which carries a requiredLevel of 4 without a corresponding acceptanceCriteria field documenting the rationale for that threshold selection. Reviewers relying solely on the narrative rationale will not notice the structural gap in the acceptanceCriteria field.",
